/0841217323I55GD9846FI96KC7G6F02F5.html\" target=_blank>谈谈“为尊者讳”</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．迟泽厚<BR><A href=\"/html/yjy/2008/412/084121746EDDHK985BH9CDF1ED82DKJ9.html\" target=_blank>毛泽东把五七指示写给林彪背景考</A>．．．．．．．．．黄　瑶</P>\r\n<P><STRONG>［人物志］</STRONG><BR><A href=\"/html/rwz/2008/412/08412174427128B986K68DKEB3AFB4DJH.html\" target=_blank>宋教仁：不该遗忘的宪政精英</A>．．．．．．．．．．．陈　章<BR><A href=\"/html/rwz/2008/412/0841217535CCHA9987AF1C095K3G6HH6E.html\" target=_blank>兴衰荣辱“黄埔系”</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．徐　平<BR><A href=\"/html/rwz/2008/412/084121767C9B5C988DCFHDH7K6B7KC35.html\" target=_blank>殉职在抗日前线的诗人王礼锡</A>．．．．．．．．．．．谢　琰<BR><A href=\"/html/rwz/2008/412/0841217711B18AK989FGDBJBF6I87ACGK.html\" target=_blank>不负周恩来嘱托的传奇夫妇</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．杜　凌</P>\r\n<P><STRONG>［怀念集］</STRONG><BR><A href=\"/html/hyp/2008/412/08412164520F8CA59665D142B1BB54893B.html\" target=_blank>读《只唯实——阎红彦上将往事追踪》</A>．．．．．．．盛方仁<BR><A href=\"/html/hyp/2008/412/08412162744C1H99657F7C8FCEK79HBJ9.html\" target=_blank>忆小高</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．李　普<BR><A href=\"/html/hyp/2008/412/08412164610HFDKJ967B5E8FJKC9B4G219.html\" target=_blank>永久的青年</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．瞿独伊</P>\r\n<P><STRONG>［文荟苑］</STRONG><BR><A href=\"/html/wehy/2008/412/08412164810GGF2D969AC4IJBH0E0A2DBD.html\" target=_blank>《在太行山上》的词作者桂涛声</A>．．．．．．．．．．刘大明<BR><A href=\"/html/wehy/2008/412/084121648552B48B970DA3J0D22E8JD60I.html\" target=_blank>华侨歌唱家黄源尹的坎坷人生</A>．．．．．．．．．．．梅门造<BR><A href=\"/html/wehy/2008/412/084121649316A2C39711EB349EI50KJ745.html\" target=_blank>邓子恢巧释“空城计”</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．棲梧老人<BR><A href=\"/html/wehy/2008/412/0841216474KBKKK9682G8I772GFHHCBJ7.html\" target=_blank>王森然先生轶事二则</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．李郁秀</P>\r\n<P><STRONG>［遗闻录］</STRONG><BR><A href=\"/html/ywl/2008/412/08412165137C5JEA972J6G32H75H32DEGH.html\" target=_blank>大清国第一任出洋钦差是美国人</A>．．．．．．．．．．孙闻浪<BR><A href=\"/html/ywl/2008/412/084121652107C2F7973EHJ82B006AKHH2B.html\" target=_blank>中英西藏战争百年祭</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．彭　苏</P>\r\n<P><STRONG>［文配画］</STRONG><BR><A href=\"/html/qyt/2008/412/084121652475BJ06974HAGB1G0A3JAI0C1.html\